    <date day="27" month="March" year="2012"/>
    <abstract>
      <t>The Generic Security Services API (GSS-API) provides a simple naming
   architecture that supports name-based authorization.  This document
   introduces new APIs that extend the GSS-API naming model to support
   name attribute transfer between GSS-API peers.</t>
    </abstract>
